result.name: Single-nucleotide polymorphism matrices for 812 plant genetic resources and 298 European elite materials of barley
result.description: Whole-genome-sequencing performed for 1,110 barley genotypes, including 812 plant genetic resources (288 spring type and 524 winter type) from German Federal ex situ Genebank for Agriculture and Horticultural Crops at the Leibniz Institute of Plant Genetics and Crop Plant Research (IPK), and 298 European elite materials (128 spring type and 170 winter type).
result.center: IPK Gatersleben - Leibniz Institute of Plant Genetics and Crop Plant Research
